    "body": "Hi @dylanpinn I did what you said: activating urlSync on the tourism example, going to page 2, page 3, then hitting the back button. And it worked, the styling is badly done because both page 3 and page 2 would be shown as \"active\". But that's only styling, the page was refreshed with hits from page 2.\n\nLet me know if you have another way to trigger the bug.\n\nThanks\n",
